reviews.review_text: Sound's pretty good, show has its moments Nice to have a good audience of the only show I made it to that tour.  They actually were playing pretty well throughout, but kept cutting songs short, especially Uncle John's>Playin'>Uncle John's.  The Dew is excellent, however.  Watch out for Looks Like Rain -- you might want to turn down the bass or risk blowing your speakers!  It's bombs away for Phil in the big city.
